    "finalTextLength": 1262,
    "finalText": "I have a synced Outlook inbox snapshot for **bclymer@alleatogroup.com**, but it’s **stale**.\n\nThe latest sync completed **May 18 at 1:24 PM ET**, so I can’t reliably tell you your true last five emails after that point.\n\nWhat I can confirm from the latest synced threads after that cutoff is the most recent visible five threads:\n\n1. **A new Capital One document is ready for you**  \n   - From: Capital One <capitalone@notification.capitalone.com>  \n   - Received: **May 18, 12:55 PM ET**\n\n2. **Re: RI-3959-0012 May Final Pay App**  \n   - From: Kebba Mass <kmass@alleatogroup.com>  \n   - Received: **May 18, 12:35 PM ET**  \n   - Thread had **4 messages**\n\n3. **Re: Interview Follow Up - Jon Knapp**  \n   - From: Jonathon Knapp <jonathon.knapp@icloud.com>  \n   - Received: **May 18, 12:19 PM ET**\n\n4. **Re: Cover Story Feature for Brandon Clymer in The Prime Today Magazine**  \n   - From: Maria Calcetero <mcalcetero@alleatogroup.com>  \n   - Received: **May 18, 12:15 PM ET**  \n   - Thread had **3 messages**\n\n5. **RE: clinic location**  \n   - From: Steve Sharp <ssharp@financialguide.com>  \n   - Received: **May 18, 12:12 PM ET**  \n   - Thread had **6 messages**\n\nIf you want, I can also give you the **last five individual messages** instead of grouped threads.",
